{
  "stem": "10862.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While my sister Mindall and I were sitting and they were bombing the camp, the Germans were already running away because they knew what was coming.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister Mindall said to me, Reva, you are a little girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why don't you go out to the kitchen and see if we can find any food?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Being a 12-year-old little girl at that time, I didn't pay much attention.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, OK, I'll run into the kitchen, because the Germans were already leaving.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was such complete chaos in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went into the kitchen, and unfortunately I did not find any food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no bread or anything left at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, I mean, I could have been killed because the bombs were falling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were bombing the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my sister Mindall sends me out to look for food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I ran out to the kitchen and, of course, I came back, there was no food, there was nothing left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we stayed that whole night in the camp while the Germans were bomb-- the Russians actually were bombarding the camps and the city.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were waiting and waiting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then finally on January 17th of 1945 in the morning, we found that the people were not taken away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were caught on the train because the Germans-- the Russians were too close so they could not be transported anymore, and then they let the people out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So all the people that were taken away that evening came back into the camp, but, of course, at that point we were already free because we were liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that's not the end of the story either, because the problem was when we were liberated, everybody was running in different directions.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
